title: TV | Marvel's Agents of SHIELD
text: Three seasons in, Agents of SHIELD shows absolutely no signs of stopping whatsoever. If anything, it seems to be just now gathering pace. So what's happening this time around? In the aftermath of the battle with Jiaying and her Inhuman army, Coulson and his team organise an international search for other people with special powers. However, the agents soon discover that SHIELD is not the only organisation that has taken an interest in the rise of superhuman abilities.
